text: Ängby SK is a sports club in Vällingby in Sweden. It was established in 1956. The club won the Swedish national men's table tennis team championship in the years of 1992 and 1995. The women's team won the Swedish national championship during the season of 2014-2015. Jan-Ove Waldner and Mikael Appelgren have played for the club. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1956 establishments in Sweden Category:Sports clubs in Stockholm Category:Table tennis clubs in Sweden
